    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>Your training and reflexes allow you to react swiftly to avoid an opponents' attacks.</em> <br /><br /></p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites</strong></p>\n<p>Dex 13.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p class=\"stat-block-1\">You gain a +1 dodge bonus to your AC. This bonus&nbsp; increases&nbsp; to&nbsp; +5&nbsp; against&nbsp; attacks&nbsp; of&nbsp; opportunity&nbsp; caused&nbsp; when&nbsp; you&nbsp; move&nbsp; out&nbsp; of&nbsp; or&nbsp; within&nbsp; a&nbsp; threatened&nbsp; tile. A condition that makes you lose your Dex bonus to AC also makes you lose the benefits of this feat.</p>",
